  @{"  Important!       " link NOTES}    Read This NOW!

  New:

  Version 1.5: Added a custom button that can be used from the
               'Msg reader' and 'Message list' button banks to
               call MD2V*

  Version 1.4: Further streamlining and enhancements. Removed the
               call 'WAITFORPORT' because some people reported
               problems with it (replaced with the wait() command)

  Version 1.1: fixed a possible guru condition! Yikes! If you used
               version 0.80 or 1.0, then upgrade NOW!

  Version 1.0: changed the way Voyager starts, MD2V will wait for
               Voyager to start instead of using a requestor (if
               automatic is chosen).

               If V is started from disk, i.e. V isn't already
               running, the message is not sent to a new window.

*If used from the 'Message list' a message still has to be selected.
